# Voice Character Color Scheme

Each voice character has a distinct color. Use these consistently:

| Character | Color | Tailwind Classes |
|-----------|-------|------------------|
| Rachel | Pink | `bg-pink-400 hover:bg-pink-500` |
| Sh | Teal | `bg-teal-400 hover:bg-teal-500` |
| Arnold | Emerald | `bg-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-500` |
| Marin | Violet | `bg-violet-400 hover:bg-violet-500` |
| Alloy | Amber | `bg-amber-400 hover:bg-amber-500` |
| Ash | Stone | `bg-stone-400 hover:bg-stone-500` |
| Ballad | Sky | `bg-sky-400 hover:bg-sky-500` |
| Coral | Coral | `bg-coral hover:bg-[#e07360]` (custom) |
| Shimmer | Fuchsia | `bg-fuchsia-400 hover:bg-fuchsia-500` |
| Cedar | Green | `bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700` |

## Custom Color

Coral is defined in `layout.css`:

```css
@theme {
  --color-coral: #eb8374;
}
```

## Usage

Use the same colors in both `voiceOptions` and `errorVoiceOptions` arrays.
